snippet.title: BUTTERFLOWERS RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
https://funsworkings.itch.io/butterflowers

⚘
Spring renews from Winter in a few frames luminous GANHUA tulips grow at the corners now in a hyperlapse (expecting)
From a telephone post all I can see is the motion white, yellow, blue pixelated fields easing between 2 points
that cold, black oooze spills over my feet Fills the loose wrinkles in the bag
looped actions unfeeling , limiting run infinite between frames they are mutated then re-compiled
60fps
⚘

: CREDITS :

AUDIO - CERTAIN LIVES (https://certainlives.bandcamp.com​)

GOBLIN IMAGES SOURCED FROM MODELS - "003 Goblin" BY CENTRIXE (https://www.models-resource.com/3ds/miitopia/model/22530/),  "Goblin Model" by Justin712 (https://www.turbosquid.com/3d-models/free-goblin-character-3d-model/457224), "Goblin" by Northern Duke (https://www.turbosquid.com/3d-models/goblin-max-free/944458)

SAMPLES - "Airplane Cabin.wav" by Filmbrute (https://freesound.org/people/Filmbrute/sounds/223684/), "Dial Tone" by ramicio (https://freesound.org/people/ramicio/sounds/158427/)
